title: 15 Give and Take: The Revolutionary Path to Success with Adam Grant
description: What if I told you the key to success was not going after what you wanted, but helping others get what they wanted instead? Better yet, what if there was research that proved the more you gave of your time and resources willingly to others, that you'd be on your way to achieving your wildest […]
